title: Grammys 2017: Flume wins award for best dance album for Skin
text:
Twins for the Clooneys 
It has been confirmed that Amal Clooney is expecting twins with husband George Clooney. Vision Channel Seven More videos Entertainment news highlights 
Donald Trump declares war on Australia, Melissa McCarthy gives his Press Secretary Sean Spicer the SNL treatment and Tziporah Malkah, formerly Kate Fischer opens up on The Project . 
Flume, whose real name is Harley Streten, shot to fame in 2012 after his debut self-titled album became number one on the ARIA Albums Chart. 
Never Be Like You received a nod this year from Triple J, taking out the number one spot in this year's Hottest 100. SHARE
